  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together flour, sugar, and a pinch of salt.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together melted butter, lime juice, and orange marmalade.",
    "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and stir until just combined.",
    "Fold in the papelon and mix until coated evenly.",
    "Pour the mixture into a greased 9-inch round cake pan.",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes or until a toothpick inserted comes out clean.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool in the pan for 5 minutes before transferring to a wire rack to cool completely."
